{"tid":1881402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】配額曝光！克警獲發64萬個外科口罩僅次醫護 N95口罩多達1.3萬個 衞生署僅獲分配不足300個N95","createTime":"2020-02-15T13:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T12:14:56.000Z","uid":78519,"like":8,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"923e7092f0bb39f524443935c12d07ee7389f17c","tid":1881402,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T13:55:34.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》獲悉，在政府首輪分配抗疫物資中，衞生署獲發最多外科口罩，數量逾130萬個；警務處排名第二，獲發近64萬個。N95口罩方面，警方獲發數量更是眾部門之冠，竟然多達1.3萬個，而衞生署僅獲分配不足300個N95。文件又披露各部門預計之後的物資使用量，其中警方更預期，2月至4月需要2.6萬件保護袍（Gown）、逾4萬件全身防護衣（Protective Coverall Suit）。相比之下，衞生署預期需要7萬件保護袍，2,000多件全身防護衣。<br />\n<br />\n其他紀律部隊包括入境處、海關、消防處，裝備待遇明顯不及警方優厚，而攸關市政清潔的部門如食環署，據悉獲發外科口罩僅及警方一半。近日警方多次出勤時，佩戴全套保護裝備，已被外界質疑其防護規格較醫護人員更高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200215/GJCE533Z6OXSN4IHEE63VYBLIM/?fbclid=IwAR0KkDk1ha3iklFU_UugM20YsslJbCDnLwv6jNpKUBic5j5fOp1O3qkiJaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200215%2FGJCE533Z6OXSN4IHEE63VYBLIM%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0KkDk1ha3iklFU_UugM20YsslJbCDnLwv6jNpKUBic5j5fOp1O3qkiJaw&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx4hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=7faca5b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200215%2FGJCE533Z6OXSN4IHEE63VYBLIM%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0KkDk1ha3iklFU_UugM20YsslJbCDnLwv6jNpKUBic5j5fOp1O3qkiJaw&h=04cb082b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200215/GJCE533Z6OXSN4IHEE63VYBLIM/?fbclid=IwAR0KkDk1ha3iklFU_UugM20YsslJbCDnLwv6jNpKUBic5j5fOp1O3qkiJaw</a>"},{"pid":"c091b1203a545ed97817504909c4ccd4f6012fa7","tid":1881402,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T13:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f406e3d01caf15e7669ccddf764aad761b12e774","tid":1881402,"uid":252492,"